comments: Wainright (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Johnson (SAS) and absorbs the contact.
As Walker IV (SAS) is losing possession of the ball during his drive, he and Bridges (PHX) engage in incidental foot to foot contact.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Jones' (SAS) off-arm before blocking the shot attempt.  The contact to the shooting hand of Jones is considered incidental.
Primo (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position, and cleanly blocks the shot attempt near the basket by Wainright (PHX).
Wainright (PHX) makes marginal contact to Jones' (SAS) body during his drive that does not affect his SQBR. Jones is able to move through the contact and make the pass to his teammate.
Booker (PHX) legally contests Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Wainwright (PHX) does not touch the ball after Vassell's (SAS) shot attempt goes off of the rim and out of bounds.  Possession is correctly given to the Suns.
Primo (SAS) grabs Booker's (PHX) right arm and affects his ability to get to the inbound pass.
Primo (SAS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Primo (SAS) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Johnson (SAS) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
